sentences: Julia Kadel (born 1986 in Berlin-Kreuzberg) is a German jazz pianist and composer.
She studied psychology at Humboldt University of Berlin, then went on to study jazz piano at the Hochschule f√ºr Musik Carl Maria von Weber in Dresden from 2009 to 2014.
She led a trio with the German-Norwegian bassist Karl-Erik Enkelmann and Dresden drummer Steffen Roth.
